And maybe there's a
little one right there.

108
00:06:20,173 --> 00:06:22,497
Got two big ones, so,
invariably sooner or later

109
00:06:22,497 --> 00:06:24,218
there's gonna be a little one.

110
00:06:24,218 --> 00:06:25,218
There he is.

111
00:06:30,333 --> 00:06:34,333
Let's fill him in, make
him just a touch darker.

112
00:06:37,483 --> 00:06:40,816
Maybe we'll put a third one right there.

113
00:06:47,925 --> 00:06:52,092
Work that in a little bit,
create a shadow behind the tree.

114
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:54,834
Okay.

