00:12:04,330 --> 00:12:06,580
All the little bushy areas.

196
00:12:12,684 --> 00:12:15,601
Maybe some little touches out here.

197
00:12:23,403 --> 00:12:24,236
Okay.

198
00:12:25,682 --> 00:12:28,932
Now let's take some more Van Dyke brown

